  "task": "Edit the Godot project at /home/user/godot_projects/signal_quit_game/.\n\n1. In /home/user/godot_projects/signal_quit_game/main.tscn, add a [connection] entry that connects the QuitButton's 'pressed' signal to the root Root node's method '_on_quit_button_pressed'. The connection block must look exactly like:\n\n[connection signal=\"pressed\" from=\"QuitButton\" to=\".\" method=\"_on_quit_button_pressed\"]\n\n2. In /home/user/godot_projects/signal_quit_game/scripts/root.gd, implement:\n\nfunc _on_quit_button_pressed() -> void:\n\tget_tree().quit()\n\nKeep the existing 'extends Control' line. Save both files.",
